ry_screen.dart`:\n40\t   ```dart\n41\t   import 'package:flutter/material.dart';\n42\t   import 'package:cached_network_image/cached_network_image.dart';\n43\t   import 'package:flutter_animate/flutter_animate.dart';\n44\t   import 'package:folio/theme/app_theme.dart';\n45\t\n46\t   class LibraryScreen extends StatelessWidget {\n47\t     const LibraryScreen({super.key});\n48\t\n49\t     @override\n50\t     Widget build(BuildContext context) {\n51\t       final theme = Theme.of(context);\n52\t       final colorScheme = theme.colorScheme;\n53\t       final textTheme = theme.textTheme;\n54\t\n55\t       return Scaffold(\n56\t         // ... mechanically converted from glossary elements\n57\t       );\n58\t     }\n59\t   }\n60\t   ```\n61\t\n62\t4. **Update router** — Add route to `lib/router/app_router.dart`:\n63\t   ```dart\n64\t   GoRoute(\n65\t     path: '/library',\n66\t     builder: (context, state) => const LibraryScreen(),\n67\t   ),\n68\t   ```\n69\t\n70\t5. **Verify** — Run `dart analyze lib/screens/library/library_screen.dart`\n71\t\n72\t## Reference Skills\n73\t\n74\t- Read **flutter-building-layouts** for constraint rules (constraints down, sizes up), avoiding unbounded constraints in flex boxes, and when to use `Expanded` vs `Flexible` vs `SizedBox`.\n75\t- Read **flutter-animating-apps** for Hero transition setup, implicit vs explicit animations, and staggered animation patterns.\n76\t\n77\t## Quality Gates\n78\t\n79\t- **No hardcoded colors** — `Color(0xFF...)` and `Colors.blue` are banned; use `colorScheme.X`\n80\t- **No hardcoded text styles** — `TextStyle(fontSize: 16)` is banned; use `textTheme.X`\n81\t- **No hardcoded spacing** — `EdgeInsets.all(16)` is banned; use `AppTheme.spaceMd`\n82\t- **No Container abuse** — prefer `SizedBox`, `Padding`, `DecoratedBox` when Container is overkill\n83\t- **Use const** — `const` constructor wherever possible\n84\t- **Trailing commas** — on every parameter list\n85\t\n86\t## Success Criteria\n87\t\n88\t- `lib/scr